'Inamorat' explores our need to give love, whether to another human being, pets, or even inanimate objects (such as prized possessions or digital pets) and also our tendency towards destruction and/or losing interest in people or things outside of ourselves. 

The score is for three layered bass viol parts and a vocal line.
